org.vadere.simulator.projects.io

Class IOOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.simulator.projects.io.IOOutput

  • public abstract class IOOutput
extends java.lang.Object
    This IOUtility class provides all methods to load, delete, list, clean output directories. Each output directory contains two fiels *.scenario and *.trajectories.
